{"tid":2099194,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周浩鼎涉UGL文件事件　調查報告指不足以構成譴責","createTime":"2020-07-08T05:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T05:28:38.000Z","uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f00796bb7773396114913e2d4ab665bb9d804388","tid":2099194,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"民建聯議員周浩鼎2017年擔任立法會涉及前特首梁振英的UGL事件專責委員會副主席期間，被揭發他提交的文件曾被梁振英修改。立法會之後根據《議事規則》就譴責周浩鼎議員的議案，成立調查委員會。調查委員會今日發表報告，結論是所確立的事實不足以構成譴責周浩鼎的理據。<br />\n<br />\n鼎鼎吉人天相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536511-20200708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536511-20200708.htm&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=2aa78956\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536511-20200708.htm&h=84b74953\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536511-20200708.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1a6f653264db7a41e688bcc2a775dd15a7ff39a6","tid":2099194,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f00796bb7773396114913e2d4ab665bb9d804388","tid":2099194,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"民建聯議員周浩鼎2017年擔任立法會涉及前特首梁振英的UGL事件專責委員會副主席期間，被揭發他提交的文件曾被梁振英修改。立法會之後根據《議事規則》就譴責周浩鼎議員的議案，成立調查委員會。調查委員會今日發表報告，結論是所確立的事實不足以構成譴責周浩鼎的理據。<br />\n<br />\n鼎鼎吉人天相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536511-20200708.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536511-20200708.htm&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=2aa78956\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536511-202